race.description: Greenwell Point Bowling & Sports Club Maiden Handicap
race.comment: FLORAL LEGEND (3) has been racing consistently peaks for a Sydney barn off narrow defeats at Goulburn. Has the rails gate and has plenty of early tow. Collett is a key jockey engagement and she sets a decent standard. Tough to beat. FIERCE IMPULSE (9) debuts and is also in a smart metro stable. The trials have been good and JVO rides from a handy gate. A bold run looks on the cards. SIMPLY NUTBUSH (1) resumes and has been racing in stronger. Has an awkward barrier and brings a big Warwick Farm trial win and has to be kept safe. ELLISMAYNE (5) is an improver in good hands and look for him to come late.
